{"type":"assistant","message":{"type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"おめでとうございます (おめでとうございます — congratulations)! ✅\n\n**Summary of what was implemented:**\n\n- **`LinearApi::fetch_pull_request_url(issue_id)`** — new trait method + `LinearClient` implementation that queries Linear's GraphQL API for issue attachments, returning the first GitHub PR URL found\n- **`FakeLinearApi::push_pr_url()`** — test helper to enqueue PR URL responses\n- **`o` → `g` keybinding** — in the `awaiting_open` state, pressing `g` fetches the selected issue's PR URL from Linear and opens it with `open`\n- **Status bar** — updated in both `my_issues` and `detail` views to show `g`ithub PR alongside `l`inear\n- **3 new tests** for the fake API's PR URL behaviour (116 total, all passing)"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":545,"cache_read_input_tokens":92014,"output_tokens":215,"max_tokens":168000,"service_tier":"standard"}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"T-019cff75-b403-719e-bd95-464d8c088f28"}
